inputanalyticsd(8) System Manager's Manual inputanalyticsd(8)

NAME

inputanalyticsd — User Input Diagnostics and Usage

SYNOPSIS

inputanalyticsd

DESCRIPTION

inputanalyticsd is a daemon that collects diagnostics and usage data on user input locally for users that have opted in.

There are no configuration options to inputanalyticsd, and users should not run inputanalyticsd manually.

SEE ALSO
